{"tid":1181891,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"[小眾音樂]有冇人聽開同人純音樂?","createTime":"2019-06-01T21:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T00:26:59.000Z","uid":193548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06ad91376490f2d429fdce283371a55357e3b02d","tid":1181891,"uid":193548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:21:40.000Z","msg":"先問一句先，有冇啲非東方為主嘅團體/專輯介紹？最好係玩樂器嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚先<br />\n覺得下面兩個同人團體唔錯<br />\nMelodic taste 玩交響，anime song orchestra，將好多動畫op ed 交響化(雖然好多我根本未睇過)，極少數非東方嘅交響arrange，除咗哩個之外我只搵到另外一個同人狐之工作室，有個album 叫世界樹ノ記憶，都係有玩管樂<br />\n哩種Pop風格用交響方式演奏，簡單輕鬆得嚟又不失交響嘅氣勢同空間感，幾好聽<br />\n是但執首例子，創聖大天使op，本身旋律都好，交響化真係幾正。利申未睇過創聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NLUa5O_xAIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNLUa5O_xAIo&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=d4d6fcad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NLUa5O_xAIo</a><br />\n<br />\n第二個係Rig&euml;l Theatre<br />\n基本上係玩凱爾特民族風舞曲，編曲感覺同melodic taste一樣好華麗，唔再係verse chorus form但都好易入耳上腦<br />\n又是但post一個例子，又風笛又豎琴，好幻想風格，正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-I--cdqDbdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-I--cdqDbdU&d=77sZY8L1Q3njiwGc8u9yTiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=2d201627\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-I--cdqDbdU</a><br />\n<br />\n老老實實唔係啲封面比人感覺劇毒嘅話應該冇咁冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇同好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17ca69c56f2ac05418e2b07ae63da5eeb0419da","tid":1181891,"uid":56833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T23:22:02.000Z","msg":"聽開July<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e8d7a3de3182ae1ac954379a3d